{"tid":2514391,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"兩名男子愛食魚生醉蝦風乾牛肉　長期頭痛揭腦內寄生蟲多如「芝麻餅」","createTime":"2021-05-03T08:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T10:25:12.000Z","uid":271829,"like":78,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"8d4209e1b9ea3c81aec53e91ac17636b55f388fb","tid":2514391,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947490/parasite_thumb_20210503_E_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947490%2Fparasite_thumb_20210503_E_600.jpg&h=515e17d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 兩名男子長期頭痛，愛食魚生、醉蝦及風乾牛肉，揭腦內長滿寄生蟲。<br />\n<br />\n進食未熟食物有風險！內地兩名男子因愛食魚生、醉蝦及風乾牛肉等，導致腦內出現寄生蟲，其中一名的寄生蟲更多如「芝麻餅」，令人震驚。<br />\n綜合內媒報道，成都一名30歲男子小胡經常覺得頭痛。在長達半個月的疼痛後，他到醫院求診，經檢查發現腦內有3個寄生蟲病灶。原來，小胡在頭痛前曾經吃過幾次魚生，平時也愛食螺螄及醉蝦。<br />\n另外，一名40歲的張先生持續頭痛了1個月，起初只要一頭痛就會食止痛藥，但後來發現就算加大藥量，止痛效果也越來越差，於是求診。結果他的腦內同樣發現密密麻麻的寄生蟲，醫生指：「看起來就像一塊芝麻餅。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947490/CFRtBk2xXUmP4Wh9klXlLyQhJdKbSy6wQB0zFUAdMxU_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947490%2FCFRtBk2xXUmP4Wh9klXlLyQhJdKbSy6wQB0zFUAdMxU_600.jpg&h=08e8cef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張先生腦內有寄生蟲，醫生指如同一塊芝麻餅。(圖片來源：紅星新聞)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947490/4afbfbedab64034f8d766f2c550317390b551dae_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947490%2F4afbfbedab64034f8d766f2c550317390b551dae_600.jpeg&h=d49e4f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小胡愛食醉蝦。(圖片來源：紅星新聞)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947490/iStock-910042_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947490%2FiStock-910042_600.jpg&h=c2f257ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小胡在頭痛前曾經吃過幾次魚生。(iStock)<br />\n<br />\n據悉，張先生長年以來都有吃「犛牛肉乾」的習慣，即是風乾、未經過煮熟的牛肉乾。結果，寄生蟲蟲卵反復多次進入他的體內，導致腦內長滿寄生蟲。<br />\n神經內科主任醫生宋曉徵表示，寄生在2人腦內的是囊蟲，屬豬肉絛蟲的幼蟲。豬肉絛蟲為常見的人體寄生絛蟲，當人誤食生或未煮熟的含絛蟲蟲卵的肉類後，人體胃酸不能殺死蟲卵，這些卵便開始在人體消化道內發育。最終，隨血液循環進入腦部、肝臟等，引起相應疾病。<br />\n如不去除腦內寄生蟲，可誘發癲癇、視神經受損等問題。而且，一般的鹽、辣椒、料酒是無法殺死食物中寄生蟲蟲卵，所以建議大眾別在食未熟肉類、魚生、醉蝦，應將食物徹底煮熟。"},{"pid":"68f3abe32b89633b5e46c38bbc08aecb7af759da","tid":2514391,"uid":54930,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:38:14.000Z","msg":"不安<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9a45a8eb975734d7025e93f287fc0da4cb0094","tid":2514391,"uid":271397,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:38:50.000Z","msg":"點過血腦屏障？"},{"pid":"c5307408be85bb468cc6866bc2fc46d18a036119","tid":2514391,"uid":142532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4920c95814997b264a3e83c2539bfe368c2eaeac","tid":2514391,"uid":172627,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:39:35.000Z","msg":"原始人咩，唔熟都食"},{"pid":"3ea352b0313153d8565a66ba7c252d9758a0c613","tid":2514391,"uid":162558,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:40:39.000Z","msg":"韓國d 醬油蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e16f6e8bdabf2d884355134e62b857d9b0bea7","tid":2514391,"uid":199162,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3eba5abbd10994f5710626db898bb9126cecbee","tid":2514391,"uid":212704,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"其實點知自己身體有無蟲？<br />\n可能得一條未必會頭痛但又同你一齊發育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062e43004011abd6f6da57f29692f5fddbf02792","tid":2514391,"uid":10890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9d9a45a8eb975734d7025e93f287fc0da4cb0094","tid":2514391,"uid":271397,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:38:50.000Z","msg":"點過血腦屏障？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"直接咬穿BBB啦"},{"pid":"c4e649359cebc5489f9223613c5a931569c15048","tid":2514391,"uid":228894,"like":95,"dislike":1,"score":94,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"芝麻人個芝麻腦似芝麻餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce391725512692c612d4dbd6c00bef9cbc8ec830","tid":2514391,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4920c95814997b264a3e83c2539bfe368c2eaeac","tid":2514391,"uid":172627,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:39:35.000Z","msg":"原始人咩，唔熟都食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"日本"},{"pid":"3c9587b6ed629497125e0f10438037c31c0a6167","tid":2514391,"uid":149266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"要點醫？開腦？定普通杜蟲藥都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca353f7e0a609806063f83b5b1bb3d493d42ba26","tid":2514391,"uid":60164,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3ea352b0313153d8565a66ba7c252d9758a0c613","tid":2514391,"uid":162558,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:40:39.000Z","msg":"韓國d 醬油蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:49:07.000Z","msg":"迷泡撚驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaea1ab7c888e90d87585b0b