2.000Z","msg":"唔係魚生問題，係大陸處理方法有問題"},{"pid":"ba5350b4d2d77d1f85bf1ce485ec266d9ffbfef5","tid":2514391,"uid":287670,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"afe7d9c48d60996f09aa83eb892e853f731ef529","tid":2514391,"uid":112878,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:12:35.000Z","msg":"食開牛肉 <br />\n中豬肉絛蟲 即係啲牛係豬扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"我留意到嘅位都係呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食牛食海鮮但中豬寄生蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99d71dcabfe61e23418d3b65b22c86aa7d6a8e6","tid":2514391,"uid":176447,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"4920c95814997b264a3e83c2539bfe368c2eaeac","tid":2514391,"uid":172627,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:39:35.000Z","msg":"原始人咩，唔熟都食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:20:23.000Z","msg":"刺身可以經超低溫冷藏一段時間殺寄生蟲<br />\n佢啲魚生處理有問題or佢食嘅係中式魚生"},{"pid":"945519c1ed833cc13f00b804eb29cd42c1bad8c4","tid":2514391,"uid":265338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d4209e1b9ea3c81aec53e91ac17636b55f388fb","tid":2514391,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947490/parasite_thumb_20210503_E_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947490%2Fparasite_thumb_20210503_E_600.jpg&h=515e17d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 兩名男子長期頭痛，愛食魚生、醉蝦及風乾牛肉，揭腦內長滿寄生蟲。<br />\n<br />\n進食未熟食物有風險！內地兩名男子因愛食魚生、醉蝦及風乾牛肉等，導致腦內出現寄生蟲，其中一名的寄生蟲更多如「芝麻餅」，令人震驚。<br />\n綜合內媒報道，成都一名30歲男子小胡經常覺得頭痛。在長達半個月的疼痛後，他到醫院求診，經檢查發現腦內有3個寄生蟲病灶。原來，小胡在頭痛前曾經吃過幾次魚生，平時也愛食螺螄及醉蝦。<br />\n另外，一名40歲的張先生持續頭痛了1個月，起初只要一頭痛就會食止痛藥，但後來發現就算加大藥量，止痛效果也越來越差，於是求診。結果他的腦內同樣發現密密麻麻的寄生蟲，醫生指：「看起來就像一塊芝麻餅。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947490/CFRtBk2xXUmP4Wh9klXlLyQhJdKbSy6wQB0zFUAdMxU_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947490%2FCFRtBk2xXUmP4Wh9klXlLyQhJdKbSy6wQB0zFUAdMxU_600.jpg&h=08e8cef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張先生腦內有寄生蟲，醫生指如同一塊芝麻餅。(圖片來源：紅星新聞)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947490/4afbfbedab64034f8d766f2c550317390b551dae_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947490%2F4afbfbedab64034f8d766f2c550317390b551dae_600.jpeg&h=d49e4f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小胡愛食醉蝦。(圖片來源：紅星新聞)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947490/iStock-910042_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947490%2FiStock-910042_600.jpg&h=c2f257ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小胡在頭痛前曾經吃過幾次魚生。(iStock)<br />\n<br />\n據悉，張先生長年以來都有吃「犛牛肉乾」的習慣，即是風乾、未經過煮熟的牛肉乾。結果，寄生蟲蟲卵反復多次進入他的體內，導致腦內長滿寄生蟲。<br />\n神經內科主任醫生宋曉徵表示，寄生在2人腦內的是囊蟲，屬豬肉絛蟲的幼蟲。豬肉絛蟲為常見的人體寄生絛蟲，當人誤食生或未煮熟的含絛蟲蟲卵的肉類後，人體胃酸不能殺死蟲卵，這些卵便開始在人體消化道內發育。最終，隨血液循環進入腦部、肝臟等，引起相應疾病。<br />\n如不去除腦內寄生蟲，可誘發癲癇、視神經受損等問題。而且，一般的鹽、辣椒、料酒是無法殺死食物中寄生蟲蟲卵，所以建議大眾別在食未熟肉類、魚生、醉蝦，應將食物徹底煮熟。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"內地....有幾奇？"},{"pid":"a9ef5fefc8e4c00e3b7e175f1d16e075461498a7","tid":2514391,"uid":10338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:22:00.000Z","msg":"大陸人啲醉蝦用河蝦<br />\n仲要以為拎酒就殺得死啲蟲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6a9a7c9701247c78016f30371fd432409dbb43","tid":2514391,"uid":20898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXj1eudD6DU8MD4m